## Security and Compliance

### 1. Payment Security
- Use Stripe's secure payment forms
- Implement PCI compliance measures
- Encrypt sensitive customer data
- Regular security audits

### 2. Data Privacy
- Implement GDPR compliance
- Provide data export/deletion options
- Secure customer data storage
- Transparent privacy policies

### 3. Business Operations
- Set up proper accounting and invoicing
- Implement tax collection for different regions
- Create refund and cancellation policies
- Establish customer support processes

This comprehensive subscription system will provide a solid foundation for monetizing your SaaS platform while ensuring a great user experience and maintaining security and compliance standards.
